race.comment: BACKSTAGE (1) just ran into one better at the Gold Coast when resuming and will have taken benefit from that hit-out. Has placed around this circuit and will appreciate the step-up to the 1350m journey now. Placed to advantage and expecting a big run. The well-related GALVANIZE (2) (half to G3 winner Extreme Warrior) looked handy saluting at Rockhampton on debut and winning hoop Wiggins stays on board. Will take a lot from that race day experience and can go back-to-back without shocking. XTRA LA VITA (12) also hails from a handy family (half to G3 winner Lightinthenite) and may run a race while fresh. GREY IMPACT (14) will be ready to peak now third-up and gets 3kg off with the claim. In the mix. STABILIZER (15) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
